        {
            "title": "陳虹秀暴動案重審罪成 社工註冊局：仍待判刑 未審議其社工續期申請",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"陳虹秀暴動案重審罪成 社工註冊局：仍待判刑 未審議其社工續期申請\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d8496d826e8c60bd2442496c0f8a281e/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031317544012900.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">陳虹秀暴動案重審罪成 社工註冊局：仍待判刑 未審議其社工續期申請</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>社工陳虹秀被控2019年在灣仔參與暴動，重審後裁定罪名成立。勞工及福利局局長孫玉菡昨日（12日）表示，社工的註冊或續期需要跟隨《社會工作者註冊條例》要求，條例訂明如果犯上指明罪行，社工註冊局要按法律要求要履行職責，相信註冊局會依法依規處理續牌申請，包括被裁定暴動罪成的陳虹秀。社工註冊局今日（13日）回覆《星島》查詢時指，由於該個案仍待法院判刑，故註冊局在現階段並未審議該續期申請。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/society/3436558/831%E7%81%A3%E4%BB%94%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%A1%88%E7%99%BC%E9%82%84%E9%87%8D%E5%AF%A9-%E9%99%B3%E8%99%B9%E7%A7%80%E8%A3%81%E5%AE%9A%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC%E5%80%99%E6%87%B2\">8.31灣仔暴動案發還重審 陳虹秀裁定暴動罪成還押候懲</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"sthl-ll\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135550/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"社工陳虹秀暴動罪成還押候懲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/397309de45f5c6dc0d1a1d2b9c2c4f2b/2025-03/NY250311WC106.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        社工陳虹秀暴動罪成還押候懲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>社工註冊局發言人表示，《社會工作者註冊條例》（《條例》）第20條（1）條就註冊期滿及續期作出以下規定，名列註冊紀錄冊為註冊社會工作者的人，註冊有效期為12個月，自他獲得註冊當日起計；的註冊可應該人的申請每年續期。\n\n</p>\n<p>發言人表示，在一般情況下，當註冊局收到並無任何被檢控及/或被定罪的續期註冊申請，局方約需十個工作天處理有關申請。若申請個案涉及被檢控中的罪行，則需待司法機構作出判決後，方能按《條例》第17條就註冊資格的規定，個別考慮該人的續期申請。\n\n</p>\n<p>記者︰黃子龍\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2057962/即時-港聞-陳虹秀暴動案重審罪成-社工註冊局-仍待判刑-未審議其社工續期申請",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-13 18:01:30",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "西九龍公路奪命車禍｜對面線泥頭車司機直擊全程 嘆「本來好小事」",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bf9883b826320c89e54eb76b8861f6fe/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250313/_2025031317462778079.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>西九龍公路一部消防車，停泊路邊處理一宗泥頭車撞水馬意外時，一部客貨車從後猛撼消防車，44歲客貨車司機重創不治。當時身處對面線的泥頭車司機講述事發經過，坦言「本來好小事」，其後「突然『嘭』一聲」便發生意外，車禍巨響之大，當時已令他感覺客貨車司機兇多吉少。\n\n</p>\n<p>泥頭車司機高先生事件中沒有受傷，他坦言「其實本來好小事」，稱自己當時由長青隧道而來，準備前往港島載貨，至現場時「有個黑影撞埋嚟，類似麻鷹，好大隻，俾佢嚇一嚇」，因而意外撞到水馬。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135334/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"61歲姓高的泥頭車司機憶述事發經過。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ddac89c46a058b85e6a261c599244ec1/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_151553390_mp4_snapshot_01_30_433.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        61歲姓高的泥頭車司機憶述事發經過。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4135335/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"61歲姓高的泥頭車司機憶述事發經過。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fb19bd047ff10cce12ab37fa26835156/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250313_151553390_mp4_snapshot_00_02_739.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        61歲姓高的泥頭車司機憶述事發經過。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134944/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"對面線一輛泥頭車撞毀水馬。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/800e490f58fbdd9cc46988f0087cbc77/2025-03/07_8.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        對面線一輛泥頭車撞毀水馬。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134942/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"對面線曾發生一宗交通事故。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/efb61c0057d2fdc6da9639e75d3fecd8/2025-03/05_14.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        對面線曾發生一宗交通事故。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134939/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方在場調查。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bdb4164e98e8b8fb05cf520e378ae2e0/2025-03/02_25.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方在場調查。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>高先生憶述，報警求助後5至6分鐘多部消防車到場，其中對面線涉事消防車停車，消防員落地到其身旁，檢查他是否有受傷，大概5至6分鐘後「突然間嗰邊『嘭』一聲」，便見客貨車便撞到消防車。高先生續指，在場消防員見狀，著他不要離開後，便隨即趕至另一側救援。\n\n</p>\n<p>高先生稱，由於自己當時位置被消防車阻擋，看不到意外經過及客貨車損毀情況，但當時已感覺客貨車司機兇多吉少，「聽見嗰啲撞擊聲，我睇（客貨車司機）都有啲危險」。最終，客貨車司機惜告不治。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/breaking-news/3437222/%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E5%85%AC%E8%B7%AF%E5%AE%A2%E8%B2%A8%E8%BB%8A%E6%92%BC%E6%B6%88%E9%98%B2%E8%BB%8A%E8%BB%8A%E5%B0%BE-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB\">有片｜西九龍公路客貨車撼消防車車尾 司機送院後不治</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>事件發生於今日下午2時許，一輛泥頭車沿西九龍公路往九龍方向行駛，至油麻地支路附近時失控，掃毀50個水馬。61歲姓高的泥頭車司機沒有受傷，報警求助。消防接報到場處理事件，其間一輛消防車停在西九龍公路往新界方向的路面，一輛客貨車駛至，猛撼消防車車尾。客貨車車頭嚴重損毀，爛如廢鐵，44歲姓張司機一度被困，其後由消防員救出，由救護車送院搶救，惜告不治。 \n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134742/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防員將被困司機救出。 fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a2cc0717e5beee4229fd40a8d67cd989/2025-03/01_26.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防員將被困司機救出。 fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134938/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方在場調查。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e1e5242c618f919cbd82b58028d67dbc/2025-03/01_27.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方在場調查。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134940/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"客貨車猛撼消防車。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6c7e002eddaaa3de3692d30c55a73c1f/2025-03/03_24.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        客貨車猛撼消防車。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134941/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f672ee40f3a968b8f222cc8a799d0c27/2025-03/04_20.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134943/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7e76d086fd526138d19abd7a247f6ffb/2025-03/06_9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134945/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"西九龍公路來回線先後發生兩宗車禍。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/864f500b89fa960c388c4d947774ba8f/2025-03/08_9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        西九龍公路來回線先後發生兩宗車禍。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134946/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"客貨車損毀嚴重。許文光攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fca732907fc2fc109255a3d85a0acf38/2025-03/09_9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        客貨車損毀嚴重。許文光攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134915/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"客貨車車頭嚴重損毀。讀者提供\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bba68181cf57aa6ff7605662f0fc9fc8/2025-03/04_1_7.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        客貨車車頭嚴重損毀。讀者提供\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134743/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防員將被困司機救出。 fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9b1550659642fc5d7e71b38879a984f1/2025-03/02_24.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防員將被困司機救出。 fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134744/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防員將被困司機救出。 fb：車cam L（香港群組）\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ea224d00bb691070eeb4aa5c3fc8a5d6/2025-03/03_23.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防員將被困司機救出。 fb：車cam L（香港群組）\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4134745/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"客貨車司機昏迷送院，搶救後不治。林思明攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2132ed516224f2f38bb176827748bbca/2025-03/04